23:09.041 --> 23:09.708
EXCUSE ME.

23:09.708 --> 23:10.834
IF YOU HAVE A SECOND,

23:10.834 --> 23:12.792
COULD YOU TELL YOUR SISTER
I WORK HERE NOW,

23:12.792 --> 23:14.250
BECAUSE SHE'S NOT LETTING ME
IN THE KITCHEN.

23:14.250 --> 23:15.625
[SIGHS]

23:18.208 --> 23:19.291
I'M GLAD I READ IT,
ACTUALLY.

23:19.291 --> 23:22.250
BECAUSE NOW I REALIZE I...

23:22.250 --> 23:25.875
