TO LEAVE, I WILL.

23:48.250 --> 23:49.333
NO, NO, NO,
THAT'S OKAY.

23:49.333 --> 23:51.250
ACTUALLY, YOU'RE
THE ONLY PERSON

23:51.250 --> 23:52.834
THAT I RECOGNIZE HERE,

23:52.834 --> 23:54.125
AND I ASK YOU,
HOW SAD IS THAT?

23:54.125 --> 23:55.291
DON'T WORRY.

23:55.291 --> 23:56.583
PARTIES ALWAYS TAKE
A WHILE TO GET GOING,

23:56.583 --> 23:57.542
THOUGH YOU MIGHT'VE

23:57.542 --> 23:59.291
WORKED A DEEJAY
INTO YOUR BUDGET.

23:59.291 --> 24:00.250
CAN'T SAY IT HASN'T
BEEN PLEASANT

24:00.250 --> 24:01.333
TALKING TO YOU,

24:01.333 --> 24:02.250
BUT DON'T YOU THINK

24:02.250 --> 24:03.667
YOU SHOULD GET OUT
AND MINGLE

24:03.667 --> 24:04.959
AND MEET SOME
NEW PEOPLE?

24:04.959 --> 24:06.291
YEAH, I PROBABLY SHOULD,

24:06.291 --> 24:08.333
BUT NEW PEOPLE
MAKE ME NERVOUS.

24:08.333 --> 24:09.917
I NEVER KNOW
WHAT TO SAY,

24:09.917 --> 24:15.000
AND THEN, EVENTUALLY,
I JUST CLAM UP TOTALLY.

24:15.000 --> 24:16.500
YOU JOKING?

24:16.500 --> 24:17.583
BECAUSE YOU HAVEN'T
STOPPED TALKING

24:17.583 --> 24:20.250
SINCE THE MOMENT
I MET YOU.

24:20.250 --> 24:21.083
WELL, YOU DON'T MAKE ME NERVOUS.
YOU MAKE ME MAD.

24:21.083 --> 24:23.291
MAD BEATS NERVOUS.

24:23.291 --> 24:25.875
OKAY, WHY DON'T YOU
JUST GO MINGLE NOW, YEAH?

24:25.875 --> 24:26.959
