27:30.417 --> 27:31.792
NOTHING.

27:40.792 --> 27:41.959
FIRST FIGHT?

27:41.959 --> 27:42.583
WHAT?

27:42.583 --> 27:44.208
WITH YOUR BOYFRIEND.

27:44.208 --> 27:46.208
HARDLY.

27:48.708 --> 27:49.917
ACTUALLY, UM, YEAH.

27:49.917 --> 27:53.250
I MEAN, AS GIRLFRIEND
AND BOYFRIEND.

27:53.250 --> 27:54.750
I MEAN, AS FRIENDS,
WE FOUGHT CONSTANTLY,

27:54.750 --> 27:57.500
BUT IT'S DIFFERENT
NOW, SO...

27:57.500 --> 27:58.542
WHICH MEANS YOU
HAVEN'T HAD

27:58.542 --> 28:00.000
YOUR FIRST MAKE-UP,
EITHER.

28:07.208 --> 28:08.375
GO AHEAD. I'LL LOCK UP.

28:08.375 --> 28:10.625
I CAN'T.

28:10.625 --> 28:13.041
BESSIE WOULD KILL ME,
BUT THANKS.

28:13.041 --> 28:15.417
WHAT, YOU THINK I'LL MAKE OFF

28:15.417 --> 28:17.500
WITH YOUR SECRET RECIPE
FOR TARTAR SAUCE?

28:17.500 --> 28:19.125
IT'S NOT THAT GOOD.

28:19.125 --> 28:21.625
HUH.

28:21.625 --> 28:24.250
DO YOU THINK YOU CAN HANDLE IT?

28:24.250 --> 28:27.250
