LOCK THE DOOR...

28:31.208 --> 28:33.333
WHAT THE HELL. THANKS, JACK.

28:33.333 --> 28:35.291
I'LL SEE YOU.

28:35.291 --> 28:38.417
BYE.

28:38.417 --> 28:41.291
[PAN CRASHES]

28:43.542 --> 28:46.375
