I DON'T KNOW

28:48.583 --> 28:49.708
WHAT'S GOING ON
BETWEEN US,

28:49.708 --> 28:51.708
BUT OBVIOUSLY
I'VE DONE SOMETHING

28:51.708 --> 28:52.708
TO PISS YOU OFF.

28:52.708 --> 28:53.792
