28:53.792 --> 28:54.959
I CAN'T IMAGINE
WHAT THAT WOULD BE.

28:54.959 --> 28:56.041
LOOK, I'M ABOUT
TWO SECONDS AWAY

28:56.041 --> 28:57.166
FROM BLOWING IT
WITH JOEY.

28:57.166 --> 28:58.083
YOU AND I

28:58.083 --> 28:59.250
KNOW EVERYTHING
ABOUT EACH OTHER,

28:59.250 --> 29:00.708
AND I REALLY NEED
YOUR ADVICE.

29:00.708 --> 29:02.208
OKAY. YOU KNOW EVERYTHING
ABOUT ME, HUH?

29:02.208 --> 29:04.125
YOU KNOW HOW I GOT
THIS SCAR ON MY CHEEK?

29:04.125 --> 29:05.708
OR THE REAL REASON
MY FATHER HATES ME?

29:05.708 --> 29:07.208
OR WHY I RIDE
THE FINE LINE

29:07.208 --> 29:08.208
BETWEEN INSECURITY

29:08.208 --> 29:09.291
AND SUPREME
SELF-CONFIDENCE?

29:09.291 --> 29:10.875
BECAUSE CORRECT ME IF I'M WRONG,
DAWSON.

29:10.875 --> 29:13.333
YOU DON'T KNOW THE ANSWER
TO ANY OF THOSE QUESTIONS.

29:13.333 --> 29:14.458
IN FACT,

29:14.458 --> 29:16.291
I'LL BET YOU DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHEN I WAS BORN.

29:18.125 --> 29:19.166
OH, MY GOD.

29:19.166 --> 29:20.250
