29:38.166 --> 29:38.750
YOU AND ME WILL DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT.

29:38.750 --> 29:40.375
OKAY, LISTEN.

29:40.375 --> 29:41.500
SEE THIS LOOK
ON MY FACE

29:41.500 --> 29:42.667
THAT I'M TRYING
SO HARD TO CONCEAL?

29:42.667 --> 29:43.875
IT HAS NOTHING TO DO
WITH MY BIRTHDAY,

29:43.875 --> 29:44.917
IT HAS NOTHING TO DO

29:44.917 --> 29:46.250
WITH GETTING
MY DRIVER'S LICENSE,

29:46.250 --> 29:47.417
AND IT CERTAINLY
HAS NOTHING TO DO

29:47.417 --> 29:48.792
WITH ROAD-TRIPPING TO MAINE.

29:48.792 --> 29:51.125
IT HAS TO DO WITH
THE STARK REALIZATION

29:51.125 --> 29:52.834
THAT EVERYBODY IN CAPESIDE
HAS WRITTEN ME OFF

29:52.834 --> 29:54.458
AS A MAN
NEITHER WORTHY OF THEIR TIME

29:54.458 --> 29:55.959
OR THEIR CONCERN,

29:55.959 --> 29:58.083
AND THE CONCLUSION
THAT I CAME TO TODAY,

29:58.083 --> 30:00.000
ON MY 16TH BIRTHDAY, DAWSON,

30:00.000 --> 30:01.667
IS THAT MY BEST FRIEND
IN THE WORLD

30:01.667 --> 30:05.125
LOOKS AT ME THE VERY SAME WAY.

30:08.041 --> 30:10.208
PACEY, PACEY...

30:10.208 --> 30:12.291
