30:12.291 --> 30:14.083
YOU CAN'T, OKAY?
EVERYTHING'S DIFFERENT NOW.

30:14.083 --> 30:15.250
YOU'VE GOT JOEY,

30:15.250 --> 30:17.417
AND OUR FRIENDSHIP
JUST CAN'T COMPARE

30:17.417 --> 30:19.458
