MAYBE ALL MY DREAMS ARE BOGUS
AND...

34:57.792 --> 34:59.458
MAYBE ONE DAY,

34:59.458 --> 35:01.583
THERE'S GOING TO BE PEOPLE
LINED UP FROM HERE TO HOLLYWOOD

35:01.583 --> 35:03.875
TO TELL ME THAT.

35:03.875 --> 35:06.875
I JUST NEVER THOUGHT
YOU'D BE ONE OF THEM.

35:06.875 --> 35:08.166
DAWSON,

35:08.166 --> 35:09.417
I'M NOT GOING
TO LET YOU OFF THE HOOK

35:09.417 --> 35:10.750
FOR WHAT YOU DID.

35:10.750 --> 35:12.750
I MEAN, IT WAS WRONG OF YOU
TO GO INSIDE OF MY HEAD

35:12.750 --> 35:13.917
AND TAKE
MY THOUGHTS AND MY FEELINGS

35:13.917 --> 35:15.041
WITHOUT MY CONSENT.

35:15.041 --> 35:16.875
I KNOW. BELIEVE ME, I KNOW.

35:16.875 --> 35:18.792
I'M SO SORRY I EVER READ THEM.

35:18.792 --> 35:21.875
AND THOUGH I DON'T OWE YOU
ANY EXPLANATION,

35:21.875 --> 35:25.417
I DO OWE YOU THE TRUTH,

35:25.417 --> 35:28.917
BECAUSE I HAVE ALWAYS
BEEN HONEST WITH YOU,

35:28.917 --> 35:32.375
BUT THE TRUTH IS, UH...

35:37.875 --> 35:42.333
I'VE HAD THESE FEELINGS FOR YOU
FOR SO LONG, DAWSON.

35:42.333 --> 35:44.667
I MEAN,

35:44.667 --> 35:47.542
THIS HIDDEN YEARNING
THAT I'VE BEEN SQUELCHING,

35:47.542 --> 35:49.792
AND...

35:49.792 --> 35:52.333
I DON'T KNOW, SOME DAYS,
IT WOULD MAKE ME JUST SO MAD,

35:52.333 --> 35:54.625
AT ME AND US,

35:54.625 --> 35:57.875
AND I HAD TO TAKE IT SOMEWHERE
AND UNLEASH IT.

35:57.875 --> 35:58.834
IT'S MY WAY OF COPING.

35:58.834 --> 36:01.333
IT'S WHERE I GO
TO TRASH LIFE,

36:01.333 --> 36:04.583
AND SO IT'S NOT
NECESSARILY THE TRUTH.

36:04.583 --> 36:05.875
IT'S JUST HOW I'M FEELING

36:05.875 --> 36:09.792
ON THAT PARTICULAR DAY
AT THAT PARTICULAR TIME, AND...

36:09.792 --> 36:12.333
LOOK,

36:12.333 --> 36:14.500
I SAVE THE TRUTH FOR YOU,
DAWSON.

36:17.500 --> 36:21.542
I HAVE ALWAYS BELIEVED IN YOU.

36:24.333 --> 36:25.333
I MEAN,

36:25.333 --> 36:28.041
YOU'RE THE MOST...

36:28.041 --> 36:32.375
EXTRAORDINARY, TALENTED PERSON
THAT I'VE EVER MET.

36:36.834 --> 36:40.708
I'M YOUR BIGGEST FAN.

36:43.458 --> 36:47.792
I'M GLAD I DON'T KNOW
EVERYTHING ABOUT YOU,

36:47.792 --> 36:50.000
BECAUSE...

36:50.000 --> 36:53.542
EVERY DAY, YOU...

36:53.542 --> 36:55.458
AMAZE ME.

37:01.041 --> 37:02.208
GOOD.

37:18.375 --> 37:20.417
[RETCHING]

37:25.250 --> 37:26.875
OH, GOD...

37:30.000 --> 37:31.333
YOU CAN BET THOSE TWO

37:31.333 --> 37:33.375
WON'T BE THE
POSTER COUPLE

37:33.375 --> 37:35.041
