MUCH LONGER.

37:35.041 --> 37:38.583
WHAT, JOEY AND DAWSON?

37:38.583 --> 37:39.667
YEAH, RIGHT.
SHE'LL HOLD OUT,

37:39.667 --> 37:43.041
AND THEN HE'LL JUST GET
SICK AND TIRED OF IT.

37:43.041 --> 37:44.083
OH, COME ON.

37:44.083 --> 37:45.000
ALL THOSE YEARS

37:45.000 --> 37:46.792
OF SLEEPING TOGETHER
IN THE SAME BED.

37:46.792 --> 37:48.125
THERE'S NOT MUCH MORE

37:48.125 --> 37:49.875
