WHAT I MEAN.

37:51.375 --> 37:52.750
NO, NO.

37:52.750 --> 37:54.625
THEY'RE LIKE BROTHER AND SISTER.

37:54.625 --> 37:55.750
I MEAN,
DAWSON EVEN TOLD ME SO HIMSELF.

37:55.750 --> 37:58.750
HE DOESN'T EVER THINK OF HER
SEXUALLY.

37:58.750 --> 38:00.834
